    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">AS 3660.2 in-service standard</span>
      <h1>Annual termite inspection across <span class="accent">Greater Darwin</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        AS 3660.2 expects every Australian home to have a competent inspection
